== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2018年10月8日，[[特納電視網|特納電視台]]宣佈預訂整季。[[雷利·史考特|雷利·史考特]]、{{le|亞倫·葛茲考斯基|Aaron Guzikowski}}、{{le|大衛·W·扎克|David W. Zucker}}、喬丹·希恩（{{lang|en|Jordan Sheehan}}）、亞當·科布倫納（{{lang|en|Adam Kolbrenner}}）和羅賓·梅辛格（{{lang|en|Robyn Meisinger}}）擔當執行監製。前兩集由雷利·史考特將執導，亞倫·葛茲考斯基執筆劇本<ref name="Direct">{{cite web |last1=Choe |first1=Brandon |title=‘Raised By Wolves’ Sees Ridley Scott “Evolving Into New Stuff We Haven’t Seen Yet”; Watch The Trailer – TCA |url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/raised-by-wolves-trailer-ridley-scott-hbo-max-tca-1203004934/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]] |accessdate=2020-08-06 |date=2020-08-05 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807033721/https://deadline.com/2020/08/raised-by-wolves-trailer-ridley-scott-hbo-max-tca-1203004934/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。製作公司包括雷利·史考特的{{lang|en|Scott Free Productions}}以及{{lang|en|Studio T}}和{{lang|en|Madhouse Entertainment}}<ref>{{cite web |last1=Petski |first1=Denise |title=Ridley Scott’s ‘Raised By Wolves’ Lands Series Order At TNT With Scott Set To Direct |url=https://deadline.com/2018/10/ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-series-order-tnt-scott-direct-1202478427/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |accessdate=2018-10-08 |date=2018-10-08 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008210146/https://deadline.com/2018/10/ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-series-order-tnt-scott-direct-1202478427/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Porter |first1=Rick |title=TNT Orders 'Raised by Wolves' Sci-Fi Series; Ridley Scott Producing, Directing |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tnt-orders-raised-by-wolves-series-ridley-scott-set-direct-1150173 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2018-10-08 |language=en |date=2018-10-08 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008212154/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tnt-orders-raised-by-wolves-series-ridley-scott-set-direct-1150173 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Otterson |first1=Joe |title=TNT Orders Ridley Scott-Produced Sci-Fi Drama ‘Raised by Wolves’ |url=https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/tnt-ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-1202972090/ |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |accessdate=2018-10-08 |date=2018-10-08 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008211319/https://variety.com/2018/tv/news/tnt-ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-1202972090/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年10月29日，[[華納媒體|華納媒體]]宣佈劇集移至[[HBO_Max|HBO Max]]播出<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |title=Ridley Scott’s ‘Raised by Wolves’ Sci-Fi Series Moves From TNT To HBO Max |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-sc-fi-series-moves-from-tnt-to-hbo-max-1202771752/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2019-10-29 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817171809/https://deadline.com/2019/10/ridley-scott-raised-by-wolves-sc-fi-series-moves-from-tnt-to-hbo-max-1202771752/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

